text: The Xiaoxian North railway station () is a railway station of the Zhengzhou–Xuzhou High-Speed Railway in Xiao County, Anhui, China. The station will commence operation on 10 September 2016, together with the railway. ==References== Category:Buildings and structures in Anhui Category:Railway stations in Anhui Category:Stations on the Xuzhou–Lanzhou High-Speed Railway Category:Railway stations in China opened in 2016 Category:Suzhou, Anhui
title: Xiaoxian North railway station
